                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7126" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1123</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9603 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">共享衔接RPA，一屏点线通经纬——财务共享背景下A电信公司融合RPA的业务流程优化之旅</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Shared connection RPA, one screen point line through longitude and latitude ——Business process optimization journey of a telecom company integrating RPA under the background of Financial Sharing</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李永红，王一迪，徐亚静，辛艳丽</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安邮电大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">A电信公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">20 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">RPA；财务共享中心；电信企业；业务流程；西部专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">RPA;Financial Sharing Center;Telecommunication Enterprises;Operation Flow</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在全球经济化不断发展的过程中，财务共享服务这种创新的模式变成了集团企业研究财务转型的焦点，2017年，机器人流程自动化（RPA）技术开始进入国内，作为技术因素代表的RPA自动化技术发展十分迅速。近年来通信行业市场竞争压力持续增大，本案例以A电信公司为例介绍如何应用RPA技术优化其财务共享中心业务流程。首先针对A电信公司的基本情况及其财务共享中心构建和运行情况进行了介绍，接着对上线运行较早、发展较好、较为成熟的采购至应付、销售至收款和费用报销这三大业务流程进行具体研究，然后介绍了A电信公司如何应用RPA财务机器人进行优化，最后介绍利用RPA财务机器人优化的预期效果。在财会领域应用RPA技术，可以解决财务共享模式下存在的问题，有效提升业务处理效率，从而降本增效，促进财务共享中心的发展与进步，可以为其他企业提供借鉴，同时把企业的财务管理水平提升到一个新的高度。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the process of continuous development of global economy, the innovative mode of Financial Shared Service has become the focus of group enterprises&#39; research on financial transformation. In 2017, robot process automation (RPA) technology began to enter China, and RPA automation technology represented by technical factors has developed very rapidly. In recent years, the market competition pressure in the communication industry continues to increase. This case takes a telecom company as an example to introduce how to apply RPA technology to optimize the business process of its financial sharing center. Firstly, this paper introduces the basic situation of a telecom company and the construction and operation of its financial sharing center, then makes a specific research on the three business processes of procurement to accounts payable, sales to collection and expense reimbursement, which are early in operation, well-developed and mature, then introduces how a telecom company applies RPA financial robot for optimization, and finally introduces the expected effect of RPA financial robot optimization. The application of RPA technology in the field of Finance and accounting can solve the problems existing in the financial sharing mode, effectively improve the business processing efficiency, reduce costs and increase efficiency, promote the development and progress of the Financial Sharing Center, provide reference for other enterprises, and improve the financial management level of enterprises to a new level.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《机器学习与财务智能》、《管理会计理论与实务》、《财务共享》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务共享中心；业财融合；RPA；财务共享中心业务流程；业务流程优化；智能财务</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-02</td>
                            </tr>
